  "prompt": "What does \"Quora \" mean?",
  "response": "Quora is a question-and-answer platform where users can ask questions on various topics and receive answers from other users. The platform allows individuals to share knowledge and expertise in different fields, making it a rich source of information and insights from a diverse community. The name \"Quora\" is derived from the word \"quorum,\" which refers to the minimum number of members required to conduct a meeting or make decisions, suggesting the idea of bringing knowledgeable individuals together to answer questions.",
